tool_description: API that returns all baby names with the provided amount of letters
title: Baby Names

api_list.name: Get Specific List of Baby Names by Length
api_list.description: This endpoint returns all baby names with the provided number of letters (2-11)
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://baby-names2.p.rapidapi.com/names/{length}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "baby-names2.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
